-Oh, Mr. Pulitzer.

288
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:25,080
-Nakakatuwa.
-Pagnanakaw 'to.

289
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,920
Oo, malupit nga ito.

290
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,920
Ano'ng ginagawa niyo rito?
Si Mazey Day, ano?

291
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:33,440
