351
00:31:57,680 --> 00:32:00,160
Bo. Hindi, kailangan na nating umalis, Bo.

352
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:04,800
-Kailangan na nating umalis, Bo!
-Diyos ko po. Ano 'to?

353
00:32:12,720 --> 00:32:13,840
Nalintikan na.

354
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:20,240
-Bilis!
-Lintik.

355
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:22,040
-Tara na!
-Kaunti na lang.

356
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,120
Tara na!

357
