"Ihuhulog mo lang 'yan sa kawali." Hindi.

376
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:40,080
Hindi 'to tungkol sa pagpiprito ng manok.
Gigisahin mo 'yan…

377
00:34:40,160 --> 00:34:42,320
Pero dapat gawin mo 'yon ng…

378
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:45,200
Dahil 'pag hilaw 'yon, at, alam mo na,

379
00:34:46,680 --> 00:34:47,680
may mamamatay.

380
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:49,840
Ikandado mo.

381
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,480
Hoy, ano…

382
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:53,440
-Ano…
-Sige.

383
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:54,760
Ayos ka lang ba? Ano…

384
00:34:56,600 --> 00:34:57,520
