Ma'am. Ano'ng nangyari?

388
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:08,120
-Huminahon ka.
-Humingi ka ng tulong.

389
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:10,160
-Kumalma ka.
-Tumawag ka!

390
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:12,320
-Gagawin ko 'yan, pero…
-Pakiusap.

391
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:14,000
-Bilis!
-Huminahon ka muna.

392
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:17,760
Hinga muna ng malalim
at ipaliwanag mo sa akin ang nangyari.

393
