Patayin…

408
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:34,840
Pakiusap.

409
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,440
Patayin mo ako.

410
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:52,960
Pakiusap.

411
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,760
Barilin mo na lang ako.

